  "title": "Lesson 83: After the Elections",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/83－After the Elections.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.jpg",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why did Patrick keep on asking the same question?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.65,
      "endTime": 16.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The former Prime Minister, Mr. Wentworth Lane, was defeated in the recent elections.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.9,
      "endTime": 24.63
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "He is now retiring from political life and has gone abroad.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 24.64,
      "endTime": 30.49,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "My friend, Patrick, has always been a fanatical opponent of Mr. Lane's Radical Progressive Party.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "endTime": 39.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "After the elections, Patrick went to the former Prime Minister's house.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.87,
      "endTime": 46.35,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "House",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "房子"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When he asked if Mr. Lane lived there, the policeman on duty told him that since his defeat, the ex-Prime Minister had gone abroad.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.36,
      "endTime": 58.52,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "On the following day Patrick went to the house again.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.53,
      "endTime": 63.76,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "House",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "房子"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The same policeman was just walking slowly past the entrance, when Patrick asked the same question.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 63.77,
      "endTime": 72.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Though a little suspicious this time the policeman gave him the same answer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.83,
      "endTime": 80.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The day after, Patrick went to the house once more and asked exactly the same question.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.1,
      "endTime": 89.63,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "House",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "房子"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This time, the policeman lost his temper.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.64,
      "endTime": 94.33,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "'I told you yesterday and the day before yesterday,' he shouted,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.34,
      "endTime": 101.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'Mr.Lane was defeated in the elections.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.65,
      "endTime": 105.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He has retired from political life and gone to live abroad!'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.66,
      "endTime": 111.99
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "'I know,' answered Patrick,' but I love to hear you say it!'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112,
      "endTime": 117,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
